snippet.textDisplay: People seem to forget that she works for a disfunctional institution, hence all her responses were on point and honest. Any public servant can tell you how state institutions have weak internal systems so you dont blame her if the IT strategic meeting has not yet been held. Context is important, its easy to ridicule her but unless you worked at Sars, dont judge her
